<plot>A documentary about a stylish, violent sub-genre of action films: the Italian crime movies that were popular in Europe in the 1970s and then went forgotten and neglected for decades. (When these films did play in the U.S., they were sometimes misleadingly marketed as horror movies). Now, with proper DVD releases, these "Eurocrime" films have been rediscovered by hip U.S. movie fans in a major revival movement.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?183467</url></doc>
